parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the illumination of the airbag warning indicator, failure to deploy airbags in the event of a crash, or unintended deployment of airbags, which can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
the airbag warning light flashes and remains illuminated
the airbag system malfunctions
the airbag sensors need to be reset
the airbag system fails to deploy in the event of a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The defect in the wiring harness can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the illumination of the airbag warning indicator, failure to deploy airbags in the event of a crash, or unintended deployment of airbags, which can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
